The commissioner shall annually request from the Nationwide Mortgage Licensing System and Registry the following statistical information, if available, relating to the examinations taken by applicants seeking registration as a loan originator in Kentucky during the preceding calendar year:
The total number of tested individuals, along with any relevant demographic information available such as race, ethnicity, or gender;
The total number of individuals who received a passing score on the examination, along with any relevant demographic information available such as race, ethnicity, or gender;
The total number of individuals who did not receive a passing score on the examination, along with any relevant demographic information available such as race, ethnicity, or gender; and
All mean, average, or scaled scoring data.
